75
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,590
This time, how about
I hand it to you?

76
00:03:22,610 --> 00:03:23,890
Oh, I get it!

77
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:25,200
Of course you do.

78
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:28,300
I've got another soda, too,
and a pickle.

79
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:31,700
The new ones are the best.

80
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:36,300
It's supposed to rain
again tomorrow.

81
