You want to bet?

83
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:46,900
I guess I could
hold off a day.

84
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,500
It's your choice.

85
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,500
My choice.

86
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:06,500
Okay, sir.

87
