Hey.
Hey.

108
00:04:58,710 --> 00:05:01,690
You working a double?
Uh, yeah, everybody's got the flu.

109
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:03,590
I feel great.
What's up?

110
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:06,490
Uh, we got a poker game we
organize about once a month -

111
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:07,790
People from the ward.

112
00:05:07,810 --> 00:05:09,500
There's an opening
if you're interested.

113
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,190
When?
Tomorrow night.

114
00:05:11,210 --> 00:05:14,900
It's just for laughs, you know,
cool off from work - Friendly.

115
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:18,000
Friendly? How friendly?
Who's coming?

116
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:23,390
It's me, uh, Dr. Jones,
Dr. Suarez, a couple of others.

117
00:05:23,410 --> 00:05:24,490
All right, why not?
Where's it at?

118
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:25,900
Your place, 8:00.

119
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,890
we rotate hosts.

120
00:05:29,910 --> 00:05:30,990
Uh-huh.

121
00:05:31,010 --> 00:05:33,990
Sandwiches, drinks, and
something sweet, if that's cool.

122
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:35,190
Sure.

123
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:37,500
Great.
I'll tell everybody.

124
